OL,3,CTrain crew rescued from roaring
OL,4,Cwildfire in Canada
OL,6,FCrew were rescued from a wildfire that
OL,7,Fengulfed a train in Ontario, trapping
OL,8,Fthem inside.
OL,10,FCredit: Sol Mamakwa
OL,12,FTrain crew had to be rescued from a
OL,13,Froaring blaze in Ontario, Canada,
OL,14,Fafter a huge wildfire engulfed the
OL,15,Farea.
OL,17,FVideo on social media show flames
OL,18,Fraging around the train, burning the
OL,19,Fground around them, as staff inside
OL,20,Fcalled for help.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
