OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784229521
OL,3,CTrain crew rescued from roaring
OL,4,Cwildfire in Canada
OL,6,F"This could potentially overtake us
OL,7,Fhere," one of the crew could be heard
OL,8,Fsaying. "This is getting a little
OL,9,Fscary."
OL,11,FThe crew members were safely evacuated
OL,12,Fbut Canadian Rail was forced to
OL,13,Fsuspend trains in the area.
OL,15,FMore than 850 wildfires were raging
OL,16,Facross Canada on Thursday, according
OL,17,Fto the Canadian Interagency Forest
OL,18,FFire Centre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
